                                                  //| back address: 127.0.1.1; using 192.168.190.144 instead (on interface eth0)
                                                  //| 14/01/17 20:57:24 WARN util.Utils: Set SPARK_LOCAL_IP if you need to bind t
                                                  //| o another address
                                                  //| 14/01/17 20:57:25 INFO slf4j.Slf4jEventHandler: Slf4jEventHandler started
                                                  //| 14/01/17 20:57:25 INFO spark.SparkEnv: Registering BlockManagerMaster
                                                  //| 14/01/17 20:57:25 INFO storage.MemoryStore: MemoryStore started with capaci
                                                  //| ty 390.7 MB.
                                                  //| 14/01/17 20:57:25 INFO storage.DiskStore: Created local directory at /tmp/s
                                                  //| park-local-20140117205725-5846
